<figureCitation box="[893,976,521,543]" captionStart="Figs 2-7" captionStartId="14.[159,199,1332,1354]" captionTargetBox="[152,1059,201,1600]" captionTargetId="figure-2@14.[152,1059,201,1600]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="Figs 2-7: (2) Brachypipona irana nov.sp. ♀ holotype, habitus lateral; (3) Brachypipona irana nov.sp. ♀ holotype, habitus dorsal; (4) Brachypipona irana nov.sp. ♀ holotype, face; (5) Brachypipona montana nov.sp. ♂ holotype, habitus lateral; (6) Brachypipona montana nov.sp. ♂ holotype, mesosoma and tergite I dorsal; (7) Brachypipona montana nov.sp. ♂ holotype, face." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5038770" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5038770/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="1108">figs 2-4</figureCitation>
